title: Most popular online dating services in selected countries as of February 2014
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 9 different Countrys on X-axis for 6 groups Facebook, Twitter, MySpace, Shaadi, Match, and Badoo. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding Percentage of respondents.
Out of all 6 groups, Facebook had the highest Percentage of respondents in Country Vietnam and MySpace had the lowest Percentage of respondents in Country India.
In Country India, Shaadi had the maximum Percentage of respondents and it saw the lowest in Country Indonesia out of all 9 Countrys.
The maximum Percentage of respondents for Shaadi that was found in Country India was 0 times larger than the minimum Percentage of respondents observed in Country Indonesia.
